text: The National League East is a division in the MLB. All of the teams are on the east coast of the U.S. In 2007, 2008, and 2009, the Phillies won the division; they also won the 2008 World Series. The NL East is known as one of the toughest divisions in the MLB. ==Teams in the National League East Division== *Philadelphia Phillies *New York Mets *Miami Marlins *Atlanta Braves *Washington Nationals Category:National League
title: National League East
